<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="36" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="9" pageNumber="36">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="9" pageNumber="36">
This genus is placed in the 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Thripidae" genus="Megalurothrips" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Megalurothrips" order="Thysanoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Megalurothrips</taxonomicName>
genus-group (
<bibRefCitation author="Mound, LA" journalOrPublisher="Entomologica Scandinavica" pageId="14" pageNumber="41" pagination="153 - 17" title="Phylogenetic relationships between some genera of Thripidae (Thysanoptera)." volume="15" year="1981 a">Mound and Palmer 1981a</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Mirab-balou, M" journalOrPublisher="Munis Entomology and Zoology" pageId="13" pageNumber="40" pagination="944 - 952" title="The Megalurothrips genus-group in Iran (Thysanoptera: Thripidae)." volume="6" year="2011 b">Mirab-balou and Chen 2011b</bibRefCitation>
) and currently includes 10 species (
<bibRefCitation author="Mirab-balou, M" journalOrPublisher="EntomologicalNews" pageId="14" pageNumber="41" pagination="348 - 353" title="A new species and a new record of the genus Pezothrips Karny from China (Thysanoptera: Thripidae)." url="10.3157/021.122.0408" volume="122" year="2012">Mirab-balou and Tong 2012</bibRefCitation>
). Only one species, 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Thripidae" genus="Pezothrips" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pezothrips bactrianus" order="Thysanoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bactrianus">Pezothrips bactrianus</taxonomicName>
(Pelikan), has been reported from Iran (
<bibRefCitation author="Mirab-balou, M" journalOrPublisher="Munis Entomology and Zoology" pageId="13" pageNumber="40" pagination="944 - 952" title="The Megalurothrips genus-group in Iran (Thysanoptera: Thripidae)." volume="6" year="2011 b">Mirab-balou and Chen 2011b</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
